'''Lorentz's whistler''' ('''''Pachycephala lorentzi''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Pachycephalidae]]. It is found in the mid-western [[New Guinea Highlands]]. Its natural [[habitat]] is subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]]s. It was originally described as a subspecies of the [[regent whistler]]

